race.comment: SET TO PROPHET (8) has gone close his last two at Armidale and Tamworth and has weight relief on a quick back up. He will use an inside gate to advantage and has winning claims. PUZZLE DESIGNER (1) peaks off a 1L defeat at Armidale. Has a handy 2kg allowance today and is ready to deliver. ELECTRIC EVIE (3) improved sharply at Armidale second-up, beaten just 1.2L behind Purple Esprit. Has placed 3/3 third-up and Nestor will give her every chance. MAJOR MAKEOVER (7) was quickly back on track beaten a whisker in the PUZZLE DESIGNER race. He needs to find a bit more to be winning this, but can't be ruled out.
